SDialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanted to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow everywhere! Everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery isn't bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but aren't these clothes a bit... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're rentals, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a waste if we didn't try to have fun on this trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just a natural skier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, you're too cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm getting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza... Pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't skied since middle school, but I guess I still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minori-chan, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a sports genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're pretty good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just average.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm moving forward. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lean sideways according to the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sideways...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, getting run over by a sled hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why do you have a sled?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.66,0:01:20.68,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs52.5\pos(940,525)} No Matter What
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanted to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you can't ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so smug about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one in our class who couldn't ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, skiing is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about wearing two long planks and sliding on snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was wondering too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Kitamura to teach you how to ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell is he supposed to teach me when I have a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're not getting Minorin to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, you're putting all my effort to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey! The lift is for two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to share one with Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but shouldn't you share one with Kashii?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako and I want to take pictures of each other while we're on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is that disgusting woman acting so friendly with Kitamura?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then get pissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you and Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! It's nothing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe something did...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had tea with Kitamura-kun after I bumped into him on New Year's,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we went to visit a shrine for a New Year's prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So something like that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in bed with the flu, so you didn't need the extra trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do I need an excuse anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to report every single thing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,Hey,Hey, why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell do you always screw things up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really, really annoying{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's screwing things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play weird tricks so you can hang around Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did, there's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want our friend to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I think your tricks are disgusting, and it pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn if an idiot like you gets pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.23,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a field trip, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of doing it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, are you thickheaded by nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or are you doing it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say something, just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I can't believe you're such an airhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nearly violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the first day ended like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming Kushieda's real feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip will be over before I even talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is so weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them, they look so lethargic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura didn't mention anything about visiting the shrine with Taiga to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly don't get what's going on in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sighing GET.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I saw you leave the dining hall all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been waiting for a chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto-kun and Maya-chan were fighting, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to relieve the tension between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a field trip, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want people to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the problem is that Maya-chan wants to be around Kitamura-kun or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one view of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you know why Noto-kun wants to stop Maya-chan's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he misunderstood and thinks that Taiga likes Kitamura-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he wants to help Taiga, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are things about Taiga that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it's a treasure, so I'm definitely going to cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm talking about the hair clip, not myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use no matter how hard I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda can't accept my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what happened on Christmas Eve or of my one-sided feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she pretended that it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're worried about you, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you really asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kitamura, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking your clothes off all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.29,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only undressing your bottom part! How perverted are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all, you're waving it on top of Takasu's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it anymore. There's some mysterious gas in my butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By Kushieda, you mean that Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other Kushiedas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's Kushieda Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love with that weird girl for over a year! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was rejected on Christmas Eve before I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did Kushieda reject you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a girl, I would definitely go out with Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Going out with you would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's like what happened in Chushingura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Asano Takumi-no-kami, and we're the Akou Ronin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and Kushieda is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kira is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:27.61,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I even rented the DVDs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kitamura is using me as an excuse to take revenge on the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was unlocked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why is it so messy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, control yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tidy it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a navy blue camisole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a wet towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you had a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tolerate an odd number of socks, so I'm pairing them up to make them even.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Taiga of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she wipe the tatami with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't wipe your hair with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Taiga come back first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! This is the only time I've ever begged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you love taking baths, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ami-chan, your curves are great! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I never wanted to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Taiga go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came back to the room first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Kushieda, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.55,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Taiga went to the guys' room by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be together with Maruo and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you're overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be possible for Yuusaku to walk in on her and Takasu-kun doing stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were real, I would totally hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wonder what's going on in Taiga's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really interested in Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between Takasu-kun and Maruo, which one do you think is Taiga's favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be troublesome for me to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask Taiga herself when she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you've been pretty quiet since we got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm tired from skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been sleepy since we got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count on getting any sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Takasu-kun could get Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would make all these problems disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Minori-chan was dragged into her sea of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something I shouldn't have because you were spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't just stare at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and tell us, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Maya-chan has said that, what should I do, Minori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you rejected Takasu-kun before he could confess on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Did Takasu-kun confess to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ami-chan, how do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, how do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-min, why did you bring that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're always spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying it to spite you because it seems you don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun is interested in you, not Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you rejected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're just pretending to be an airhead in order to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably thinking "Let's just be friends forever."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you see me pretending that nothing has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look into my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it has nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your sense of guilt is nothing too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you at least had some feelings for Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought you'd feel guilty about {\i1}someone{\i0}, so you rejected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rejected him simply because you don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him about it tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be kinder to just end it now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to leave him half-dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at faking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we girls arguing on a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you went a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just apologize and let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Taiga isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's look for her together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kushieda, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we just witnessed something that we shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and Kushieda was a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one who doesn't get what they were arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which country was Ami-chan talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taka-chan, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we neither saw nor heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, so I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's something I have to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be my fault that Minori-chan rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something sarcastic to Minori-chan when you weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know why I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I had an argument with Minori-chan yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt pissed off whenever I saw her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because she never looked directly into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I pushed her, I couldn't find out how she really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself because I'm an idiot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt really guilty and I exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of misunderstandings, and now it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid chi-, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I told you to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are you going to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologized already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you some ice cream when we get back to the dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-min, I'm sorry for not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sorry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that you did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... I really couldn't stop{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't forgotten about what happened yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to mess things up because I was having a chat with Takasu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "what happened yesterday," you mean the thing you started?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I forgot about it you went and brought it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.90,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you forgot about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been ignoring me all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your egotistical gaze pisses me off, you brainless Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's egotistical?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just pissed off because you're jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hitting the face, Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always hated those of your kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.76,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a follow-up on yesterday's argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there and watch. Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you! I fucking hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:06.73,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the ski resort staff are out looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't find her, they're going to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip of yourself; they'll definitely find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it might be you who'll{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back when I've checked the places we've been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, tell the teacher we're going out to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some skid marks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get some adults over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left her alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has always been by my side, but I never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clumsy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of you when I catch you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji would definitely save me at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the God of Broken Hearts's blessing didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish didn't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take these feelings away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,loving Ryuuji.
